channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Fifth body found in Bayesian superyacht search as one still missing after Mike Lynch confirmed dead
item.description: A fifth body has been found after the luxury the Bayesian yacht sank off the coast of Sicily during a storm on Monday morning - with 22 people on board the vessel

item.title: Toxic chemicals that can cause brain damage found in antique books
item.description: Scientists have discovered they could be toxic and unsafe to handle.

item.title: Teen dances in haunting last TikTok before fatal Ibiza balcony fall as tributes pour in for 'angel'
item.description: University law student Emma Ramsay died after falling from a sixth floor balcony at Ibiza's Hotel Vibra District as her mum paid a heartbreaking tribute to her daughter and 'best friend'

item.title: Pope ‘hiding alien secrets in the Vatican’, UFO campaigner claims
item.description: Extraterrestrial lobbyist Steve Bassett has claimed it is clear the Catholic church knows alien life exists.

item.title: Mum given just months to live vows to make the most of her final moments
item.description: Louise Gallagher, 42, was given the devastating news that she had an extremely rare cancer of the cervix - but has vowed to make the most of her final moments with loved-ones

item.title: Warning to not eat these berries as Alicia Silverstone eats dangerous fruit on camera
item.description: They may look delicious but some of these berries are fatal so its best to heed with caution when foraging for fruits. It comes as Clueless star Alicia Silverstone shared a clip of herself eating the fruit on Monday before asking her Instagram followers what it is.

item.title: Molly-Mae Hague 'humiliated' Tommy Fury with intimate bedroom details
item.description: As Molly-Mae Hague and Tommy Fury's break-up continues to shock and bewilder fans, tongues are wagging that Tommy may have felt 'humiliated' by his ex's candid confessions about their love life
